The paper discusses the evaluation of machine learning pipelines, which falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The use of surrogate models for evaluation also relates to software engineering (cs.SE) and data structures (cs.DS). Additionally, the experiments conducted in the paper involve image classification, which falls under computer vision (cs.CV).
